@User uniform-buyer Thank you for your honest feedback and for bringing up the importance of clear consequences. I understand your frustration and the need for stronger measures in cases of repeated disrespect. I'll update the draft to include explicit examples of unacceptable behavior and present both the warning system and the option for a temporary suspension for repeat offenders. I'll also make it clear that the community has the power to request a review or escalation if they feel the response is insufficient.

A poll will be up within the next hour for you and the rest of the community to choose your preferred approach. I'll also consider your suggestion about permanent bans as an option for severe or repeated violations.

I appreciate your engagement and commitment to making this space better for everyone. Let's keep the conversation respectful as we move forward.
